   101	# <a id="_Toc207966444"></a>__2 Project Definition__
   102	
   103	## <a id="_Toc207966445"></a>__2\.01 Executive Summary__
   104	
   105	Pivot Interiors requires a unified platform to replace their current fragmented system landscape consisting of Adobe Workfront, D365, Power BI, and FluidPay for managing pre\-quote activities\. The company processes complex design and labor quote requests across multiple market segments \(Enterprise, Venture, Public Health Care, Government\) with sophisticated workflows that currently require extensive manual coordination between systems\.
   106	
   107	Orion/NetSuite provides an integrated solution that directly addresses Pivot's pre\-quote process requirements through standard request management, design workflow automation, resource capacity reporting and financial integration capabilities\. The solution eliminates manual data re\-entry between systems while maintaining the sophisticated business logic and approval workflows that Pivot has developed over several years of operations\.
   108	
   109	## <a id="_Toc207966446"></a>__2\.02 Company Overview__
   110	
   111	Pivot Interiors, Inc\. comprises a distinguished team of innovators, creators, and thought leaders dedicated to crafting exceptional interior solutions for businesses of all sizes\. Our designs not only embody your brand but also inspire employees to thrive, create, and collaborate in the workplace\. California\-born and raised, we are proudly headquartered in the Bay Area, serving clients state\-wide\. With offices and Design Centers in Santa Clara, Fremont, San Francisco, Costa Mesa, Los Angeles, and La Mirada, we invite you to explore our spaces and experience the Pivot Interiors difference\. Pivot Interiors is a MillerKnoll Certified Dealer\.
   112	
   113	[__https://www\.pivotinteriors\.com__](https://www.pivotinteriors.com/)
   114	
   115	## <a id="_Toc207966447"></a>__2\.03 Orion/NetSuite Overview__
   116	
   117	Orion/NetSuite provides a comprehensive pre\-quote management solution designed to eliminate the manual processes and system disconnects that create operational inefficiencies in project\-based businesses\. The envisioned solution includes an integrated request engine with configurable request types, conditional field visibility, and automated routing capabilities that ensure requests reach appropriate resources without manual intervention\.
   118	
   119	The resource management capabilities within Orion/NetSuite enable automated assignment workflows with real\-time capacity tracking, eliminating the manual coordination currently required between users\. Built\-in utilization reporting provides visibility into resource allocation against established targets, while integrated time tracking captures both billable and non\-billable hours for accurate project profitability analysis\. The solution's project management functionality seamlessly connects pre\-quote activities to downstream order processing and fulfillment workflows\.
