   121	## <a id="_Toc207966448"></a>__2\.04 Project Overview__
   122	
   123	Pivot’s current engagement with GSI is based around the creation and implementation of a set of business requirements appropriate to its business operations both today and scaling into the future\. This project primarily consists of the following stages:
   124	
   125	- __D__iscover: Evaluate the dealer’s business processes with Orion/NetSuite capabilities
   126	- __R__ealize: Perform initial setup, installation and configuration of your NetSuite instance
   127	- __E__ducate: Empower your team for success through comprehensive training and user adoption support
   128	- __A__ctualize: Bring your NetSuite and Orion solution to life with seamless data migration and go\-live support
   129	- __M__aximize: Support and expand your operations with dedicated ongoing assistance and strategic customizations\.
   130	
   131	Our implementation approach is “Align, Adapt, Accommodate”\.
   132	
   133	- Align – Existing processes fit in Orion/NetSuite as is\.
   134	- Adapt – Pivot will change its processes to fit in Orion/NetSuite as is\.
   135	- Accommodate – GSI will create a configuration specific to Pivot, or if the feature can benefit others, will update the code base to make the feature standard\.
